social_posts.post_text: I made it my goal to recover enough to attend Toys4Tots and participate.  It was so wonderful!  It was only possible because of the incredible love and support I received from so many.  In my darkest hours, every time I was told someone was reaching out; praying for me; or even had traveled to see me… it was then I found strength.  I now know what it is like to be on the receiving end of the most amazing parts of the car community:  it’s charity and love for one another.  I am blown away.  I love you all and I thank you.  #secondchance #lamborghinicomunity #carfriendsrule #attitudeofgratitude #Toys4Tots @uhhdope 🙌🏻🙏 so dope to be on your film 🎥 let’s do something epic in a few days 👍🏻✔️

HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME 🎂 AND THANK YOU for all the well Wishes.  We love our Instagram followers and family,.. over the years we have forged hundreds of friendship .. life long close friends .. from people we meet on IG.  We don’t monetize our content or try to get content for instagram.  We just live and the content happens. What we put up is us just living and trying to help others while having a good time.  I almost died this year in a terrible flaming car wreck. I have many emotions about that but mostly I am so grateful to have shared another year of my life with you all on the Gram.  I can’t believe there were people coming from out of state for he and I’m so touched ❤️ I feel like MOST people understand me by their comments and Conc l and I talk about our followers all the time.! We have watched some go from young car spotters to lambo owners!  I have been so proud watching my friends leveling up over the years., thank you for my Birthday Wishes.  I’m 56 and I feel 21…. With the impulse control of a 4 year old… but it’s been amazing ride.  I have changed since seeing death and I would like to devote more of my time to helping people … God bless and we are in this life together #teamsalamone #luxurylifestyle #supercarlifestyle #lamborghinistyle

#Winning always meant just living every day to the very fullest and to have the most extreme experiences while always doing good things and making true connections with other people in a way that is positive. Lamborghini was a great way to express this and to have those experiences.  Our cars have really allowed us to strive … to be WINNING … not against anyone but as a personal goal on a daily basis, and we have used them for good and for fun.  I love @lamborghini  and I don’t drive anything else.  I am loyal.  Wait till you see what we have coming. #teamsalamone #power  @teamsalamone

I thank God I am still alive.  One year ago today ..my Lamborghini was completely on fire … flames  20 feet into the air.  My hair: clothes and skin were on fire. I reached down to unbuckle the seatbelt and my skin melted on my knuckles.  Seatbelt off I opened the door and I was ripped out of the car by @porschrarri !  Mike saved my life!! I Was transported via Chopper.  I kept asking for a mirror … my scalp was partially ripped off … They said that there are no mirrors and that I would possibly lose my left eye and right ear.  I really wanted to be released, even against doctor’s orders.  On the third day I rose from the hospital.  For months Conc scraped and cleaned my wounds.  My skull was fractured badly …. I couldn’t see any good in life or anything.  I was in a very dark place.  Then, I thought of some of the brave children I met at pediatric cancer charity events. Especially  @kingfightscancer !  I drew strength from my great friend @morohoshi7777 and his incredible recovery.  Friends came to my aid from all over … even flying in. @britney_phelan @sls333blu; Dear friend and Doctor Glen Messina was there for me when I firsts woke up.  @uhhdope was always there at my side,  Sid means so much to me.  Thank you to @lamborghini @manhattanmotorcars @jaclynmariejohnston for always helping me express myself; for inspiring me and for bringing me back to the excitement and experiences that I love so much.  @joshua__kingg2 love you and thanks for collecting all my bling! @lambokid227_ @125dan125 @allout_ron @cloud9exotics @pcny @batmanrealaccount thank you for being there in my time of need.  Special thank you to my Office for keeping things going when I was down.  I feel very different now and I intend to live in the most positive way; make more of a positive impact and have more connections with people.  IT FEELS SO WONDERFUL TO BE ALIVE.  #lamborghini #supercarcrash #supercar #teamsalamone #teamsalamonethemovement #crash #supercarlifestyle #praisehim #secondchance
